Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.27,0:00:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,进来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.24,0:00:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打扰您了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.82,0:00:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们能活着回来真不简单
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.45,0:00:24.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们虽然是活下来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.42,0:00:27.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但度西斯却已经…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:29.73,0:00:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道该从哪里说起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:32.39,0:00:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,照实说就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:37.20,0:00:38.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的头脑里现在一片混乱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.87,0:00:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,诺齐亚…我们的故乡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.97,0:00:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们或许再也回不去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.94,0:00:47.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们所仅有的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.91,0:00:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只剩下\N爸爸他们留下来的先锋艇了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.60,0:01:12.83,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,just keep on trying, keep on flying\N{\c&HFFBF00&}just keep on trying, keep on flying
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:12.90,0:01:16.49,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,I will be the light\N{\c&HFFBF00&}I will be the light
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:16.57,0:01:23.77,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,如果说把黎明　当作是一个开始\N{\c&HFFBF00&}夜明けをひと　つの始まりとするなら
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:23.84,0:01:30.77,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,如果说现在就是来临的时刻\N{\c&HFFBF00&}今が来るべき時だとするなら
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.85,0:01:35.38,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,与你的烟云时代交响曲\N{\c&HFFBF00&}君とのCloud Age Symphony
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.46,0:01:44.76,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,飞向云海的彼端　飞往光芒照射的方向\N{\c&HFFBF00&}雲の海の向こうに　光が射す方へ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.37,0:01:59.73,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah～是否可以遇见有如魔法的那一刻？\N{\c&HFFBF00&}Ah～魔法のような一瞬に会えるのか？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.81,0:02:07.02,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,取代寒冷的黑夜\N{\c&HFFBF00&}冷たい夜を引き替えに
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.09,0:02:14.12,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,我俩展翅飞翔\N{\c&HFFBF00&}二人は羽ばたいて
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.19,0:02:25.07,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,在那尽头  抓住了永恒…\N{\c&HFFBF00&}永远を掴む、その果てには
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.65,0:02:41.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H8dccf0&}身不由己\NFairy chess
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.27,0:02:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要进去啰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.21,0:02:58.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舰长他想见你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.81,0:03:02.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可是有报告的义务哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.64,0:03:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克劳士他现在人在舰长室…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.05,0:03:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.38,0:03:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…不想去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.22,0:03:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不想…现在去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.43,0:03:25.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好久没看到你这种表情了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.54,0:03:30.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克劳士他人很温柔吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.58,0:03:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你出手还真狠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.72,0:03:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是因为那个驾驶员的关系吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.79,0:03:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我本来想找他谈谈的\N他却根本不理我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.29,0:03:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大新闻哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.29,0:03:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说起来这可比诺齐亚沦陷\N或者度西斯瓦解更来得大条呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.26,0:03:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们那位小公主哦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.80,0:04:01.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的不骗你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.70,0:04:03.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我从来没看过\N小公主那个样子呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.44,0:04:05.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看来她果然是跟克劳士…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.47,0:04:07.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.94,0:04:09.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我叫你们闭嘴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.48,0:04:11.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,通通闭嘴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.85,0:04:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,盖尔他当然是不高兴啰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.45,0:04:17.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为他早就看上了克劳士说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.12,0:04:18.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当心我扁你哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.85,0:04:22.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看来那小子\N也不是个省油的灯嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.96,0:04:27.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托不要再随便乱猜了好不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.13,0:04:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样拉薇未免太可怜了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.60,0:04:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莫蓝你太嫩了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.57,0:04:37.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要展开攻势的话…就趁现在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.11,0:04:43.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.38,0:04:44.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出来一下好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.21,0:04:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇，连克劳士你也不理吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.99,0:04:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她什么时候开始这样的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.32,0:04:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好一阵子了\N连回答都不回答一声
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.86,0:04:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,关于诺齐亚的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.26,0:05:00.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也和你一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.80,0:05:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚听说的时候\N我也不知该如何是好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.53,0:05:07.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们一起努力吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.80,0:05:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除了努力也没别的办法了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.54,0:05:12.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我正在修理先锋艇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.57,0:05:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇你不是常说吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.98,0:05:16.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无论发生再难过的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.71,0:05:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要埋头在机械里就可以忘记
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.28,0:05:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以说我们一起修理好不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.22,0:05:24.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一起来修爸爸他们的先锋艇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.29,0:05:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇，我也在等你哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.62,0:05:30.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.49,0:05:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给拉薇她一点时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.13,0:05:33.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.77,0:05:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.74,0:05:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你根本就没搞懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.88,0:05:51.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陛下对于你让四艘新建的\N乌尔班级战舰沉没一事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.91,0:05:54.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感觉十分的震怒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.92,0:05:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是陛下给你的处分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.62,0:06:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谨听接旨吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.02,0:06:07.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,命即刻免除\N文生．亚杰之乌尔班舰长职务
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.60,0:06:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,并立刻编入麦德赛侯爵麾下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.40,0:06:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讨伐入侵诺齐亚的度西斯残军
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.77,0:06:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,钦旨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.77,0:06:21.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,文生，虽然必须离开乌尔班号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.51,0:06:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过你不认为\N这才是一项光荣的任务吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.02,0:06:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,度西斯瓦解了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.06,0:06:39.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,银之战舰也随着EXILE之钥\N一起沉没了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.76,0:06:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搜索银之战舰的工作\N仍在持续进行中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.73,0:06:47.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在就断定钥匙已经消失\N会不会言之过早了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.30,0:06:50.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，一点也不会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.44,0:06:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.44,0:06:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基尔特公会凭藉EXILE来\N统治这世界的时代已经结束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.91,0:06:59.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,EXILE已成为过去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.78,0:07:01.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,面对毫无威胁力的统治
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.32,0:07:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们安那托勒该做的事\N只有一个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.99,0:07:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是消灭基尔特公会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.06,0:07:10.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陛下的意思是…要开战了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.13,0:07:15.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快去准备吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.65,0:07:31.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.75,0:07:33.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安，拉薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.98,0:07:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.89,0:07:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,关于船舰的修复状况
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.65,0:07:42.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目前已完成到\N足以启航的阶段了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.49,0:07:47.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,据各部门的报告，剩下的作业\N可以在出航后继续进行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.56,0:07:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.73,0:07:50.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,准备出发
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.30,0:07:53.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,动力启动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.27,0:07:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全体人员，准备出发
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.37,0:07:58.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全体人员，准备出发
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.08,0:08:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,动力启动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.51,0:08:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,齿轮传动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.92,0:08:08.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,涡轮启动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.93,0:08:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.90,0:08:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.03,0:08:23.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要一直站在那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.16,0:08:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们要不要也来\N帮忙照顾一下这小家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.23,0:08:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,组件浮力压已确保\N轮机准备OK
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.60,0:08:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舵机正常，航海准备完毕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.51,0:08:34.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所有炮门全力发射没问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.91,0:08:36.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舰炮准备完毕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.28,0:08:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先锋艇已完成固定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.71,0:08:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,随时都可以出发
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.25,0:08:41.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左方搜敌，没有敌踪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.48,0:08:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,右方搜敌，同样没有敌踪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.12,0:08:44.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.99,0:08:46.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,周遭没有动力音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.26,0:08:51.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舰长，全舰已完成出发准备
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.33,0:08:52.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出发
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.83,0:08:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,银之战舰出发
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.93,0:08:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,两舷微速，开始上升
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.77,0:08:58.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开始上升
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.73,0:09:00.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上升
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.19,0:09:24.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重新复出了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.06,0:09:26.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你没弄错吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.46,0:09:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.20,0:09:29.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已确认过克劳地亚反应
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.26,0:09:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是银之战舰没有错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.17,0:09:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目前正在玛琉山脉上空移动中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.40,0:09:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这事还有谁知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.07,0:09:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有我们和宰相阁下您
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.51,0:09:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，别泄漏出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.01,0:09:43.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有关银之战舰的一切情报\N只能向我报告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.81,0:09:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,千万不可直接告诉陛下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.51,0:09:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.48,0:09:48.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,属下遵命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.72,0:09:59.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,EXILE之钥依然安在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.83,0:10:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陛下的判断只会自取灭亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.86,0:10:05.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了避免开战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.53,0:10:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是得向公主殿下…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.51,0:10:15.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是\N塔琪安娜跟我说的全部内容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.04,0:10:18.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她其实也是很辛苦的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.31,0:10:21.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以说，塔琪安娜和我们之间\N虽然有过一些过节
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.05,0:10:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你能不能就原谅她吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.59,0:10:27.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她说话的方式是冲了一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.56,0:10:30.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过我想\N那也是因为她太认真的关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.06,0:10:34.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.46,0:10:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很希望你跟塔琪安娜之间\N能够好好相处
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.91,0:10:47.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.04,0:10:50.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.48,0:10:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克劳士…对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.02,0:10:56.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我受不了和你待在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.25,0:10:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.45,0:10:59.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.22,0:11:01.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.43,0:11:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.14,0:11:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,视线良好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.48,0:11:24.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前方没有任何飞行物体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.91,0:11:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舰长，请指示前进方向
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.38,0:11:29.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朝基尔特总帅戴芬妮处前进
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.16,0:11:38.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克劳士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.03,0:11:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾丽丝，你什么时候…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.70,0:11:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你打算去哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.34,0:11:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是要把这还给克劳士而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.54,0:11:54.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塔琪安娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.71,0:11:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你\N不要因为这件衣服而想太多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.65,0:12:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然他人的确是很温柔…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.35,0:12:03.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塔琪安娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.35,0:12:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我到拉薇那里去看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.16,0:12:11.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.73,0:12:12.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一整天没见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.26,0:12:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是发生了什么事吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.06,0:12:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.53,0:12:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.57,0:12:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自从你和红色的那个一起回来\N你就成了八卦焦点啰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.94,0:12:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且你都不跟我玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.01,0:12:28.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你懂不懂啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.78,0:12:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的工作可是要监视我耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.18,0:12:32.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.91,0:12:34.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就好好干活啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.38,0:12:35.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,休假已经结束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.52,0:12:41.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这架先锋艇\N长得和你那架一模一样呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.69,0:12:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不这么认为吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.99,0:12:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你去过诺齐亚了是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.66,0:12:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你去过诺齐亚了对不对\N镇上现在情况怎样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.43,0:12:52.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你猜错了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.00,0:12:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是我在舰长房间里找到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.47,0:12:56.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是亚力克斯的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.04,0:13:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么啦，你居然没发现啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.85,0:13:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真没意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.88,0:13:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我本来只想\N找个话题跟他聊聊的说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.89,0:13:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,进行搜敌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.02,0:13:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先锋艇队全体出击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.89,0:13:16.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.33,0:13:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚力克斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.09,0:13:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.66,0:13:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先锋艇队出击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.27,0:13:25.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.93,0:13:28.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你跟我来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.41,0:13:37.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塔琪安娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.25,0:13:41.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们帮你\N另外准备了一架先锋艇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.49,0:13:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦，恢复搭档了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.99,0:13:54.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塔琪安娜，快一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.80,0:13:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.60,0:13:59.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克劳士他今天不飞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.07,0:14:03.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以才由我们两个搭档的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.30,0:14:04.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只限今天而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.01,0:14:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好闲哪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.54,0:14:11.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们也出去搜敌你说怎样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.11,0:14:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我猜迪奥殿下\N您姊姊也正在找您吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.32,0:14:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那…还是算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.66,0:14:28.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全体先锋艇出击完毕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.50,0:14:35.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回答我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.94,0:14:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚力克斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.91,0:14:42.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无论真相是什么\N你都能接受吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.05,0:14:49.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,与其心里一直有块石头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.05,0:14:51.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我宁愿知道真相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.87,0:15:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我爸爸他们的照片\N会在你的房间里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.07,0:15:13.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你原以为是属于你父亲的\N那架先锋艇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.44,0:15:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其实是我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.75,0:15:24.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那天，告知你母亲\N飞越大风暴区行动失败的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.69,0:15:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.15,0:15:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和爸爸他们一起飞的人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.52,0:15:30.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来就是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.29,0:15:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是一条丧家之犬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.60,0:15:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夹着尾巴从大风暴区逃了回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.33,0:15:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把我最心爱的人\N就丢在了那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.97,0:15:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是说照片里\N那个和你在一起的女子吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.48,0:15:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错，我们曾互许了终生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.75,0:15:59.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有看到\N爸爸他们的最后一刻吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.09,0:16:02.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.66,0:16:05.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想我大概到死都不会忘记吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.49,0:16:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她在笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.72,0:16:36.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她看着我们笑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.76,0:16:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戴芬妮总帅…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.83,0:16:48.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.94,0:16:57.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这艘船之所以要对抗基尔特\N是为了复仇吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.75,0:17:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算是除掉了它\N也不能改变什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.78,0:17:03.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果不设法改变这个世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.88,0:17:05.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对抗基尔特就毫无意义了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.92,0:17:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,改变世界？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.32,0:17:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要能得到EXILE\N就可以改变这个世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.09,0:17:14.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,EXILE！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.23,0:17:20.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我，EXILE究竟是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.87,0:17:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基尔特公会威权的凭仗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.44,0:17:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,足以颠覆这个世界的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.84,0:17:31.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你得到那种东西…打算做什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.98,0:17:33.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要亲手来毁了它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.12,0:17:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是你飞翔在天空的理由吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.32,0:17:41.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是一切的真相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.16,0:17:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你不喜欢我的理念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.36,0:17:45.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你大可下船求去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.48,0:18:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.81,0:18:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,苏菲亚公主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.87,0:18:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起，让你操心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.90,0:18:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我变成一个令人讨厌的女孩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.71,0:18:33.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没这回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.51,0:18:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真傻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.14,0:18:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其实我只需要问他\N在沙漠里发生了什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.25,0:18:42.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要像平常一样\N轻松的谈一谈就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.58,0:18:45.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是我就是做不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.69,0:18:48.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克劳士在我看起来\N就好像变了一个人似的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.96,0:18:53.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且我就是没办法控制自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.46,0:18:56.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塔琪安娜穿着\N克劳士衣服的身影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.20,0:18:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是一直在我脑海挥之不去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.58,0:19:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,宰相他希望我能登基
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.85,0:19:19.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在期待什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.65,0:19:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道你是那种靠我的一句话\N来决定去留的弱女子吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.99,0:19:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好想一想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.70,0:19:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是为了什么才登上这艘船的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.53,0:19:33.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这不用去想就很清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.27,0:19:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这发型…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.07,0:19:39.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不适合战舰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.84,0:19:41.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.78,0:19:45.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我全都对克劳士说了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.08,0:19:47.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过他似乎不打算下船
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.82,0:19:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.84,0:20:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好香的味道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.84,0:20:14.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.11,0:20:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我擦了点香水想说换一下心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.91,0:20:19.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.42,0:20:22.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚才在走廊上…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.85,0:20:23.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克劳士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.89,0:20:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们聊一会儿吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.82,0:20:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.57,0:20:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚力克斯他之前\N为何什么都没跟我说呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.74,0:20:48.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他明明认识我，却什么都没说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.81,0:20:53.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他只是冷眼旁观\N我和拉薇在战场上备受煎熬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.48,0:20:57.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他那么做和杀了爸爸他们的\N基尔特公会有什么不同呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.02,0:21:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舰长他内心也是很痛苦的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.99,0:21:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可不这么认为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.96,0:21:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不是我把证据摆在他面前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.69,0:21:09.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他恐怕打算永远都不说出来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.46,0:21:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这才是我最不能原谅他的一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.20,0:21:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但即使如此\N你还是决定待在这艘船上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.84,0:21:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,光是看着你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.91,0:21:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就可以知道\N你父亲是个怎样的人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.21,0:21:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舰长他可是很尊敬你父亲的喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.12,0:21:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,苏菲亚你又是为了什么\N而登上这艘船的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.49,0:21:36.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.03,0:21:39.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不需要道歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.73,0:21:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我自己也很吃惊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.00,0:21:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我从没想过\N自己竟然是如此的软弱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.97,0:21:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,苏菲亚你绝对不是个软弱的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.41,0:21:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你人真的很温柔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:35.15,0:22:39.31,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,黑夜的时光逐渐逼近\N{\c&HFFBF00&}夜の時間が迫り来る
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:40.92,0:22:45.98,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,你离我如此接近感觉  却好远…\N{\c&HFFBF00&}あなたはこんな近く  でも遠い…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.06,0:22:57.13,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,你的憧憬是什么  心中想的又是誰\N{\c&HFFBF00&}何に憧れて だれを想うのか
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.20,0:23:02.73,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,你舍命奋斗的身影\N{\c&HFFBF00&}いのち賭ける姿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.81,0:23:11.51,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,有一种透明的美丽  令我不禁哑口无言\N{\c&HFFBF00&}透き通る美しさに 言葉を飲んだ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:11.59,0:23:17.46,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你欲飞往天际\N{\c&HFFBF00&}あなたが空を行くなら
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.52,0:23:23.26,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,我愿成为你的翅膀\N{\c&HFFBF00&}わたしは翼になりたい
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:23.33,0:23:29.13,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,无论风有多么强\N{\c&HFFBF00&}どんなに強い風にも
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:29.20,0:23:34.90,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,也永远不会折断的柔婉翅膀\N{\c&HFFBF00&}けして折れない しなやかな羽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:34.98,0:23:46.94,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,相信有一天  我会拥有那样一对翅膀\N{\c&HFFBF00&}いつか　きっと持つから
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.56,0:23:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（下回预告）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.53,0:23:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道枪兵的生存率是多少吗
